    "openapi": "3.0.0",
    "info": {
        "title": "Laravel Base Project API",
        "version": "1.0",
        "description": "On every index request using per_page=$number as a parameter will add a pagination override. If the parameter isn't present in the request the results will be still paginated with 25 per page. If the request needs to return multiple relationships the query parameter should be like: ?include=relationship1,relationship2. On every request that is sent you can use the include, filter and sorting query parameters. All of these query parameters are defined in a models index or get request."
